title: Complaining is Not a Strategy
itunes:title: Complaining is Not a Strategy
description:
Episode 127 - Every time you complain to take a step away from your goals. Complaining has no value. Complaining is a cancer that eats you from the inside and it is completely self inflicted. In this episode I talk about the CEO Amazon and his thoughts on complaining.
